     C**************************************************************************
     C           *INZSR    BEGSR
      *
     C           P#BRC     PLIST
     C                     PARM           PMAREA100
     C                     PARM           PMBYTE  3
     C                     PARM           PMCHK   1
     C                     PARM           PMRTCD  1
